                Soli In<lb break="no" n="2"/>victo <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Sext</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Babe<lb break="no" n="4"/>rius Ianu<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ar</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): CIL III: Z. 1/2: Im/victo(!); Z. 4/5: I[a]n[u]/ar(ius)(?); CIMRM: Z. 4/5: Ianu/ar(ius); CIL III: Z. 5: v(otum) s(olvit) l(ibens) m(erito); ILJug: Z. 5: v(otum) s(olvit) l(ibens) m(erito) l(aetus).</p>
